 <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> writer <PERSON> Bruce </PERSON> <PERSON> Bartley </PERSON> is a volunteer firefighter and medic and a member of the Anchorage Critical Incident Stress Debriefing Team.
