from the firm ng parties held in May 1987 The company came under investigation for suspected bribery after it was disclosed that it sold hundreds of thousands of unlisted shares of its real estate subsidiary at discount prices to 159 influential people. The recipients of the netted substantial profits after over-the-counter trading began.
